  <div id="targetspotting">
  <ol>
<li>UK residents who travelled to North America spent (...) more money per visit than those who went to Europe.
<list class="set3task1">
<li><a id="t1">much</a></li>
<li><a id="t2">many</a></li>
<li><a id="t3">far</a></li>
<li><a id="t4">a lot</a></li>
</list></li>

<li>UK residents who travelled to EU countries spent the (...) time per visit.
<list class="set3task1">
<li><a id="t5">fewest</a></li>
<li><a id="t6">least</a></li>
<li><a id="t7">smallest amount of</a></li>
<li><a id="t8">smallest number of</a></li>
</list></li>

<li>UK residents who travelled to EU countries spent the (...) days per visit.
<list class="set3task1">
<li><a id="t9">fewest</a></li>
<li><a id="t10">least</a></li>
<li><a id="t11">smallest amount of</a></li>
<li><a id="t12">smallest number of</a></li>
</list></li>

<li>Visits to countries outside Europe lasted (...) more days than visits to countries within Europe.
<list class="set3task1">
<li><a id="t13">much</a></li>
<li><a id="t14">many</a></li>
<li><a id="t15">far</a></li>
<li><a id="t16">a lot</a></li>
</list></li>

<li>(...) UK residents went to non-EU countries than to EU countries.
<list class="set3task1">
<li><a id="t17">Far less</a></li>
<li><a id="t18">Far fewer</a></li>
<li><a id="t19">A far smaller quantity of</a></li>
<li><a id="t20">A far smaller number of</a></li>
</list></li>
<p class="linespace"></p>
</ol>
